data.description: This like new 4 bedroom 2 bath ranch home shows TLC & offers ready to move in opportunity. 1200 sq. ft. on the main floor that offers newer wood engineered flooring, almost through out home with ceramic flooring in remaining.  All interior has fresh paint along with new front door and shutters. Combination kitchen dining has custom cabinetry with all new stainless appliances and plenty of counter top space. Large living room, hall coat closet, linen closet, hall full bath, 2 bedrooms and master bedroom suite with walk in closet and full master bath. Full walk out basement with laundry area, future living space available, with rough in for 3rd bath and a true 4th bedroom with window and closet. Newer water heater, large back deck, additional side parking, 2 car garage, covered front porch, double lot has one tax id.  Nice home location is less populated, yet with all of the lake amenities. Verifying the yearly assessments.
